Features of the theme:
- Opening each time a new tab, enjoy the new bright wallpaper Rainbow Six Siege;
- Choose a wallpaper from many available wallpapers Rainbow Six Siege when opening a new tab.
- The theme has quick access to your bookmarks and Gmail mail;
- On the new tab there are icons for quick access to social networks of YouTube, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, as well as to large online stores AliExpress, Amazon, Ebay.
- The new tab also has a digital clock, the weather in real time with the definition of your location;
- The theme is used by the Google search engine;

The new Chrome tab changes the standard Chrome page on Rainbow Six Siege theme with HD wallpapers.

